<br>
BTW, &quot;/ all GUILD&quot; will even show anon people, but you can't use the various race/class/level search parameters on it when folks are anon or role.  Some folks only come to raids that drop loot for them.  It's a great way to catch people trying to skip out and hide from raids.  Also, the leader could make up long lists of &quot;/ all foo&quot;,&quot;/ all bar&quot;,etc. and spread them across several macros to find all the people of a particular class.<br>
